#

French Onion Burger

35 min
$12.5
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinContains Dairy

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

AmericanComfort FoodGrillingBeef

Description

A juicy beef burger topped with caramelized onions and melted cheese, bringing classic French flavors to your backyard grill.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • burger buns: 4
  • onions: 2 large
  • gruyere cheese: 4 slices
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • thyme: 1 tsp
